<p><strong>The Sacred Djehuti</strong><br />
<strong>Authors:</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lt-flops" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1735419); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1735419&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1607469339" alt="Lt Flops" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1735419)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lt-flops" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1735419); return false;">Lt Flops</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ayers" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1856789); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1856789&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1607469339" alt="Ayers" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1856789)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ayers" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1856789); return false;">Ayers</a></span><br />
<strong>Published on 12 Jun 2018</strong></p>
<p>This article is <strong>Part 8</strong> of the <strong>Team Bird</strong> storyline.</p>
<hr />
<div style="font-weight: bold; text-align: center;">
<p>More by these authors:<br />
<span style="font-size:130%;"><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/floppyphoenix" target="_blank">Lt Flops</a><br />
<a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/ayers-array" target="_blank">Ayers</a></span></p>
</div>
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></div>
