<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/bird">▸ More by this Author ◂</a></p>
<hr /></div>
<div class="translation_block">
<h1 id="toc0"><span>Translations:</span></h1>
<div class="list-pages-box">    <div class="list-pages-item">


<p><iframe src="http://interwiki.scpdb.org/?wiki=scp-wiki&amp;lang=en&amp;page=_default:the-sacred-djehuti" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="" width="" class="" style=""></iframe></p>
